1148
01:30:13,600 --> 01:30:15,600
 Ja se sjećam, jedne godine nam postiramo.

1149
01:30:15,600 --> 01:30:16,600
 Smo mi bili.

1150
01:30:16,600 --> 01:30:18,600
 Plesao se po stolu u konobismo.

1151
01:30:18,600 --> 01:30:19,600
 Da.

1152
01:30:19,600 --> 01:30:20,600
 Da.

